3D FPZ cube (periodic, random field) — slab-isotropy test
domain 3
diam 0.01 maxiter 10000 perflag 3 1 1 1 ranint -2 ranflag 0
nvertex 2 ncurve 0 nsurface 0 nregion 1 ninclusion 0 ncontrolvertex 0
# bounding-box corners widen the localiser so periodic partners can be found
vertex 1 coords 3 -0.01 -0.01 -0.01 refine 1. radius 0.
vertex 2 coords 3  0.11  0.11  0.11 refine 1. radius 0.
prism 1 box 6 0. 0. 0. 0.1 0.1 0.1 refine 1.
